cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with Reinforcement Learning algorithms. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as RL is a subfield of AI. The paper also involves analyzing the convergence rate of SA algorithms, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, since the paper deals with RL algorithms, it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
